	<h1 class="title">美国儿童选择奖快要改名为美国女孩选择奖了</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
				<span class="name">杨茜</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-03-30 17:14:26 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/7930/medium/7930.jpg?1436694998" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


